                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>delay but cannot now help it.<lb/> I have not collected any money for<lb/> your a/c\n                save <persName>Mr. Morrison's</persName> since my last<lb/> report, but I keep\n                firing notes. <persName>Mitchell<lb/> Hart</persName> is a hard knot, but he has the\n                redeem<lb/>ing quality of being good natured and<lb/> prolific in promises.\n                    <persName>P. J. Joachimson<add>?</add></persName>. <persName>A<lb/>\n                        Kursheedt<add>?</add></persName> and many others pay no at<lb/>tention to my\n                notes. I have kept my son<lb/> busy in <hi rend=\"underline\">trying</hi> to collect\n                something, but without<lb/> success. <persName>Louis Austin<add>?</add></persName>\n                says he has not had<lb/> the Occident since <date>1858</date>. How is it?</p>\n            <p>Remember me most kindly to <persName>Mr. Cozens</persName> and<lb/>\n                <persName>Ella</persName> who have my best wishes for health<lb/> and happiness and\n                when they wrote to<lb/>\n                <persName>Dr Wolff's</persName> family. I should like much to<lb/> be kindly\n                remembered to them also.</p>\n            <p>I was glad to meet <persName>Ella</persName> at <placeName>Norwalk</placeName><lb/>\n                several weeks since. She is certainly very<lb/> interesting and attracted much attention<lb/>\n                <persName>Mr. H &amp; M Salz<add>?</add></persName> always deserves to be\n                remembered<lb/> with best wishes for your health and<lb/> prosperity</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I remain as ever</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Yours sincerely</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">H. S. Hanford</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p\n                rend=\"The following is written sideways over the previous text at the left side of the page\"\n                >Who is it that you are <sic>cudgelling</sic> so lustily<add>?</add> about your<lb/>\n                Hebrew College? You are very severe in your last article<lb/> I congratulate you on\n                the political changes now being<lb/> developed throughout the <placeName>Northern\n                    States</placeName>, <placeName>Pennsylvania</placeName> and\n                    <placeName>Ohio</placeName> in particular. I only hope the Ball may be kept<lb/>\n                rolling till the <hi rend=\"underline\">mad radicals</hi> of the dominant party<lb/>\n                are forever put to silence.</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
